 *   prerequisites to any combat scenario.
 * - @ref tutorial_spatial_world — AoE combat queries use the
 *   spatial index to find targets within range.
 * - @ref tutorial_ai_behavior — NPC targeting reads the
 *   ThreatList CombatSystem maintains.
 * - `advanced/ECS_DEEP_DIVE.md` — System dependency graph and
 *   parallel scheduling.
 * - `include/cgs/game/combat_types.hpp` — `DamageType`,
 *   `CastState` enum layout.
 * - `include/cgs/game/combat_system.hpp` — `DamageCalcParams`
 *   and the public API.
 */
